interest_explanation: Replicate has launched a new AI API platform, allowing users to run and fine-tune AI models with ease. The platform supports various models and tasks, including image and video generation, and provides a simple API for deployment and customization.
interest_drivers: Introduction of a new AI API platform
Support for various AI models and tasks
Easy deployment and fine-tuning of custom models
